title: Personalised Wedding Day Slippers for Bridesmaids, Wedding Party, Hen Party, Bridal Party
description:
Beautiful personalised wedding slippers perfect for the morning of the big day, Hen party or any other occasion!

Adult slippers are ONE SIZE ONLY and will fit up to a UK size 8-9 (US 10-11)

Very soft and comfortable open toe white spa slippers.

Can be customised to how you would like!

**HOW TO ORDER**

1. select quantity/role and text colour required

2. Please include personalisation details AND DATE OF WEDDING/EVENT in the box provided below (the date WILL NOT be included on the slippers unless specifically requested)

**IMPORTANT**

These are hotel/spa Slippers and are considered to be 'disposable'. As such, they are not intended for, and will not withstand regular use. They are intended for light use around hotel/spa area for the day / weekend.

**DELIVERY**

All UK orders are sent via Royal Mail 1st class post.

International orders are sent via Royal Mail TRACKED delivery. You will receive your tracking information with your dispatch email via Etsy. The approximate delivery times are between 1 - 4 weeks to be delivered. LoveMimiX cannot be held responsible for delays in international delivery due to items being held in customs or postage delays within your country.

**WE ARE A UK BASED COMPANY**

If you are not 100% happy with your purchase please contact us ASAP.

Thank you for looking! Please contact us if you have an queries!
